

1) Installation for Linux
==========================

To install kannada tex run shell script install.sh

To uninstall kannada tex run shell script uninstall.sh

Please check the path inside of install.sh and uninstall.sh before running the scripts.


2) Installation for Windows
==============================

To install kannada TeX for windows run install.bat batch file.

To uninstall kannada tex run uninstall.bat batchfile.

Please check the path inside of install.bat and uninstall.bat before running the scripts.


*********************USAGE*********************************

include \usepackage{kanlel} to activate kannada as default

See examples/manual.pdf and examples/udaya.tex.

